# Design Reference — Nexus AI (https://nexusai.framer.website)

Use this reference for layout decisions, section structure, and UX patterns when adding or modifying sections.

## Global Layout Principles

- **Centered content** with `max-w-7xl mx-auto` container
- **Vertical rhythm** via consistent `py-24 sm:py-32` section padding
- **Dark background** with subtle grid or dot texture behind sections
- **Section → Label → H2 → Subtext → Content** hierarchy is universal

## Navigation Pattern

```
[Logo + brand name]  [Links...]  [CTA button]
```
- Fixed/sticky on scroll with glass effect after scrolling past hero
- Mobile: hamburger → slide-in drawer with vertical links
- CTA: primary colored button linking to external conversion URL

## Hero Section

- **Status badge** top-center: animated ping dot + short status text (e.g. "Available for new projects")
- **H1 headline** with gradient text spanning 2-3 lines, max 6-8 words
- **Subheadline** in `text-muted`, 1-2 sentences, max-w-2xl centered
- **Dual CTA row**: primary button (filled) + secondary button (ghost/glass)
- **Social proof row**: tech stack logos or client badges below CTAs
- **Background**: radial gradient aura emanating from center

## Pricing Section (from nexusai.framer.website/pricing)

Three-tier card layout:
```
[Basic]          [Standard ★ Featured]    [Premium]
────────────     ───────────────────      ────────────
Price/mo         Price/mo                 Price/mo
──────           ──────                   ──────
Spec list        Spec list                Spec list
──────           ──────                   ──────
Feature list ✓   Feature list ✓           Feature list ✓
──────           ──────                   ──────
[CTA button]     [CTA button - glowing]   [CTA button]
```

- **Featured card**: larger, ring accent border, glass-panel-strong, slightly elevated (scale or translate-y)
- **Feature comparison table** below cards (Pro / Team / Unlimited columns)
- **"Most Popular" badge** on featured tier

## Feature/Integration Grid

- Icon + title + short description cards
- 3-column desktop, 2-column tablet, 1-column mobile
- Hover: subtle glow border reveal, `-translate-y-1`
- Category labels above grid groups (e.g. "Analytics", "CMS", "DevTools")

## Testimonials

- Quote card with: avatar → name → handle → star rating → quote text
- 3-column grid or horizontal scroll carousel
- `glass-panel` background, no harsh borders

## FAQ Accordion

- Radix `Accordion` with custom trigger styling
- Question in `font-semibold text-white`, answer in `text-text-muted`
- Expand icon rotates 45° on open (`data-state="open"`)
- Border bottom appears on open state in `matrix-green/20`

## Footer

4-column layout: Brand column | Navigation | Resources | Stack/Links
- Brand column: logo + tagline + social icons
- Copyright bar at bottom with `text-text-muted text-sm`

## Newsletter CTA (bottom of pages)

- Full-width section or card with gradient border
- Email input + submit button inline
- Copy: "Join our newsletter" / "Get exclusive content"

## Micro-interactions

- All interactive cards: `transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1`
- Buttons: glow box-shadow on hover (stronger than default)
- Links: `text-matrix-green hover:text-matrix-green-light transition-colors`
- Stat counters: animated count-up on scroll into view
